item.title: Finally!!
item.description: I have been trying to setup my own site for years and I kept letting things get in the way.You know “things” like life, kids, career and all…
item.content:encoded:
I have been trying to setup my own site for years and I kept letting things get in the way.

You know “things” like life, kids, career and all the other stuff.
Well I am happy to say that I set aside some time to get this super fast static site up! I will make a post about what is under the hood soon.

I plan on posting a blend or tech, jeeps, travel and life in general. I don’t want to say how often I will post, but I will be posting often.
